    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether certain intravitreal injection techniques
      cause less pain than others and would therefore be beneficial for the patient's well being.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
