  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients receiving intravitreal anti vascular endothelial growth factor (VEGF)
             injections

          -  Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Dementia or any other reason for cognitive deterioration

          -  Technical limitations not allowing injecting by the protocol
      </textblock>
